  "remarks": "Katerina Arlamenkova is the Chair of the Crimean regional branch of the State-led youth organisation “Movement of the First”, which was created through a Presidential Decree. Under her leadership, the regional branch has engaged in the militarisation of Ukrainian children in Crimea. Moreover, “Movement of the First” has portrayed Crimea as Russian, and promoted Russian integration within the region.",
